					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"And when she does, she looks so adorable that it pisses me off even more.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"她的这副模样也非常惹人怜爱，所以才会让人更加生气。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
